{"tid":2057016,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】可囚10年 王宗堯劉頴匡等人涉7.1闖立法會 律政司將改控暴動罪","createTime":"2020-06-09T05:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T05:45:35.000Z","uid":224375,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2c2671864bc0e7f589b41c284c9986cda1430230","tid":2057016,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T05:45:35.000Z","msg":"去年7.1反送中遊行，示威者闖入立法會，並一度佔領會議廳。警方去年8月底開始拘控多人，包括社運人士劉頴匡、港大學生會前會長孫曉嵐以及藝人王宗堯等人，並控以進入或逗留在會議廳範圍罪，案件早前定於明天再訊。劉頴匡及孫曉嵐今早在fb貼文，指接獲律師通知，控方將申請改控涉案人士較重的暴動罪；據了解，藝人王宗堯亦屬其中一員。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200609/MSDPRDIWHE7HWWEKIFUTPIV2PU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=telegram\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200609%2FMSDPRDIWHE7HWWEKIFUTPIV2PU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtelegram&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelg3kfWbBCvxMfTTNG0K1D1Y%3D&h=e1184364\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200609%2FMSDPRDIWHE7HWWEKIFUTPIV2PU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtelegram&h=fc4c9e1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200609/MSDPRDIWHE7HWWEKIFUTPIV2PU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=telegram</a>"}]}